   43                           ;; Define the IRQ handlers to be a simple
                                 branch to hal Isr routines.
   44                           ;; This method allows CMSIS Device IRQs to
                                 remain as-is while supporting
   45                           ;; legacy hal ISRs and not pushing/popping any
                                 stack behavior as a result
   46                           ;; of interrupt routines.
   47                           ;;
   48                           
   49                           ;; A trampoline function from Reset_Handler to
                                 halEntryPoint is not necessary.
   50                           ;; The Source/IAR startup code must instantiat
                                e the Reset_Handler and as
   51                           ;; a consequence the functon halEntryPoint is
                                 not used.
   52                           
